{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"7e6617c6-a0a1-56f0-9fda-fc0eb489d10a","excerpt":"问题描述 列表 FlatList 直接放在 View 里面，无法 pull to refresh 原因排查 因为 FlatList 基于 ScrollView 和 VirtualizedList 封装，查看了 ScrollView 的官方文档说明 Keep in mind…","html":"<h5 id=\"问题描述\"><a href=\"#%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E6%8F%8F%E8%BF%B0\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>问题描述</h5>\n<p>列表 FlatList 直接放在 View 里面，无法 pull to refresh</p>\n<h5 id=\"原因排查\"><a href=\"#%E5%8E%9F%E5%9B%A0%E6%8E%92%E6%9F%A5\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>原因排查</h5>\n<p>因为 FlatList 基于 ScrollView 和 VirtualizedList 封装，查看了 ScrollView 的官方文档说明</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Keep in mind that <strong><code>ScrollViews must have a bounded height in order to work, since they contain unbounded-height children into a bounded container (via a scroll interaction)[1]</code></strong>.\nIn order to bound the height of a ScrollView, either set the height of the view directly (discouraged)\nor make sure all parent views have bounded height. <strong><code>Forgetting to transfer {flex: 1} down the view stack can lead to errors here, which the element inspector makes easy to debug</code></strong>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h5 id=\"解决方案\"><a href=\"#%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>解决方案</h5>\n<p>在 FlatList 外层的容器里加上<code>{flex：1}</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\"><pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"gatsby-highlight-code-line\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>View</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">style</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>flex<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\"></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">  </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>FlatList</span>\n    <span class=\"token attr-name\">...</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\"></span>\n<span class=\"token plain-text\"></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>View</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<h5 id=\"问题引申\"><a href=\"#%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E5%BC%95%E7%94%B3\" aria-hidden class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>问题引申</h5>\n<ol>\n<li>FlatList 和 ScrollView 都必须包裹在有<strong>确定高度</strong>的容器内才能正常工作<br>\n所以，如果 FlatList 内嵌在 ScrollView 里，或者反之，内嵌的控件无法正常工作，因为 FlatList 或 ScrollView 都是不固定高度的。\n之前也遇到过类似情况，无意中将 FlatList 放在了基于 ScrollView 封装的容器里，只要上拉加载更多，就会出现 FlatList 无穷加载的情况</li>\n<li>FlatList 和 ScrollView 都必须放在<code>{flex:1}</code>的容器里，否则无法正常工作</li>\n</ol>","frontmatter":{"date":"May 19, 2018","title":"使用FlatList(ScrollView)的一个小问题","image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.5056179775280898,"src":"/static/9983387778f1c70c0ce32374522d12c6/d7b72/post-default-bg.jpg","srcSet":"/static/9983387778f1c70c0ce32374522d12c6/2347c/post-default-bg.jpg 750w,\n/static/9983387778f1c70c0ce32374522d12c6/5a448/post-default-bg.jpg 1500w,\n/static/9983387778f1c70c0ce32374522d12c6/d7b72/post-default-bg.jpg 3000w,\n/static/9983387778f1c70c0ce32374522d12c6/439d2/post-default-bg.jpg 4288w","sizes":"(max-width: 3000px) 100vw, 3000px"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/Blog/FlatList和ScrollView的一个小问题/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/Blog/CST与GMT的差别/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"CST与GMT的差别"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/Blog/使用json-server搭建API模拟服务器/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"使用json-server搭建API模拟服务器"}}}}